13.

<span id="fn_394"></span>[112:13](sbe30036.htm#fr_394.md) Chap. 3, 16.

<span id="fn_395"></span>[112:14](sbe30036.htm#fr_395.md) Chap. 3, 17 seq.

<span id="fn_396"></span>[112:15](sbe30036.htm#fr_396.md) Chap. 3, 26.

<span id="fn_397"></span>[112:16](sbe30036.htm#fr_397.md) Comp. chap. 3,
24. 25.

